    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365770/extras/e16d61299af37b123d94a06996d27dab.avif?t=1759229580\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO THE VOLUME</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Robert Locksley, and this heist will change everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Volume</i> is a near-future retelling of the Robin Hood legend, starring BAFTA-winner Danny Wallace (<i>Thomas Was Alone</i>), Charlotte McDonnell, and award-winning, critically-acclaimed actor Andy Serkis (<i>The Lord of the Rings, Planet of the Apes</i>) as Gisborne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover, then unravel, the exploitative plots of Gisborne Industries by using the Volume to pull off increasingly ambitious heists. Challenge a corporate leviathan with stealth action – it doesn't matter how many guards Gisborne posts if none of them know you are there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak, distract, avoid. As you grow in notoriety, so will your inventory. An arsenal of gadgets await discovery in a quest to rob from the rich and give to the unheard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365770/extras/89c84641f3ed10d267c745db03860231.avif?t=1759229580\" width=780 height=100 /></span>Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 levels of pure stealth action, unlocking a suite of gadgets as you go to avoid, distract and evade detection. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three modes to play your way: <strong>Freedom </strong>(checkpoints always enabled), <strong>Lockdown </strong>(checkpoints disabled while being pursued), and <strong>Execution </strong>(checkpoints always disabled).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full suite of easy-to-use tools to build and share your own levels with the world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack composed by David Housden (<i>Thomas Was Alone</i>) that mixes the futuristic setting of Volume with its Robin Hood inspiration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starring Andy Serkis (<i>The Lord of the Rings, Planet of the Apes</i>), Danny Wallace (<i>Thomas Was Alone</i>), and Charlotte McDonnell.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365770/extras/121d0689b307c8098950a62c2a482b98.avif?t=1759229580\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p></li></ul>",
